CodeDef mac Filter
CodeDef mac Description UNIX/DOS to Mac OS newlines
CodeDef mac Routine <<EOR
sub {
	my $val = shift;
	$val =~ s/\r?\n|\r\n?/\r/g;
	return $val;
}
EOR
